@startuml GUI_CRC

title GUI — CRC Diagram

class GUI {
  == Responsibilities ==
  Build and display the login panel (logo, fields, buttons)
  Build and display the chat panel (message area, input, controls)
  Collect credentials and delegate login to Client
  Collect credentials and delegate registration to Client
  Delegate outbound text messages to Client
  Render incoming Message objects in the chat area
  Show error and success status messages to the user
  Switch between login and chat screens via CardLayout
  Disconnect the client and return to the login screen on logout
  Save the chat history to a timestamped text file
  --
  == Collaborators ==
  Client
  Message
  InvalidLoginException
  RegistrationException
}

class Client {
  (collaborator)
}
class Message {
  (collaborator)
}
class InvalidLoginException {
  (collaborator)
}
class RegistrationException {
  (collaborator)
}

GUI --> Client              : calls connect(), send(), disconnect(), register() >
GUI --> Message             : renders in chat area >
GUI ..> InvalidLoginException : catches & displays >
GUI ..> RegistrationException : catches & displays >

@enduml
